Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:57.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? So, you're going to Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:00:59.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the places...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:03.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But they got good food there. And the girls are lookers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:06.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been half a year since the last war, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.58,0:01:09.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad we both survived it in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There, full house!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Tough luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:17.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.89,0:01:20.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey missy, you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.06,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Spoils from the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:27.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Caramel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:31.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't think I deserve this expensive food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:33.44,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:35.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:40.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No sweat. They say if you treat your trumpeter right, she'll play the call to retreat louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:45.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Without conscription going on, a new recruit's pretty rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:49.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I wanted to learn to play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.29,0:01:52.55,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.67,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:57.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.59,0:01:59.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private, your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:00.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a festival in Seize today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:17.15,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:19.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll stop here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:27.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Your assigned post is the Timekeeping Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:33.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Just head in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:40.96,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice of appointment, Private Sorami Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You are hereby assigned to Platoon 1121 in Trois, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Helvetia Republic Army Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:49.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,1320 hours, mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The town of lakes and glass, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:23.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I must report to my post at 1500 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:30.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I can let you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:36.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Bearing, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.52,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Current time, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Equipment, check!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:46.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:24.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful note.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,10.25 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pretty doll{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten was swept up in the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.64,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and suddenly sped off in a random direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:57.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens like to loiter on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what makes them cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:05.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Only if it's a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.70,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, this one has an owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:25.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, bring that thing over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.85,0:07:23.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{just in case}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, c'mon, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found another wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:57.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl from the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.79,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How thankful of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the flame, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:24.73,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.40,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:33.78,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.43,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:04.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You made a mess of yourself. \NWhat're you gonna do with these clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:07.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.90,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank yo{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she must've been an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you at least dodge it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:52.23,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, this dye is made to disappear once it dries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a festival, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.16,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's related to the legend of Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:08.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the fire maidens who protected this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:21.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.39,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I also took care of the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.35,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.36,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Felicia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of her business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.86,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:43.83,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late! She's late! She's so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:46.29,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I came all this way to welcome her, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present from your father, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.59,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.85,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:07.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I got myself lost along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.60,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but thanks to that, I had a wonderful encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.98,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But please don't get lost here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:41.72,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very soothing, and somehow nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:46.93,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.93,0:11:47.97,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.77,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:57.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:01.03,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to die for that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.65,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:06.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.20,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure... this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:41.94,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.11,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do, so I'm leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:45.82,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:50.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}That bell must have been important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:52.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,700)}What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.71,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.30,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:18.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.32,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fire maidens?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:22.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Long ago, when the world was much like the world today,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:29.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a winged demon settled in the valley below this town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:41.10,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This demon rained fire, shook the land, and caused great suffering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:51.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then, it took maidens living in the fortress, trapping them in a labyrinth below the earth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:02.42,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, these maidens never yielded to their fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:10.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using a golden horn entrusted by Heaven, they called out to each other and escaped the labyrinth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:16.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And with the help of a giant spider, they defeated the demon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.18,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}cutting its head to the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:24.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But suddenly, from the head came a great inferno.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:28.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Untended, the entire town would have burnt to ash.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:37.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To stop the fire from spreading, the maidens embraced the demon's head in turns.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.28,0:15:40.41,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, the burning demon's head was embraced by the maidens,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:43.92,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as the villagers poured water on them every day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:47.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Finally, after a year, the flames died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:55.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From those days hence, the water festival was held to impart some solace on these savior maidens.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:53.48,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The new girl didn't come, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.48,0:16:55.69,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.99,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Captain! It's Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:01.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks really good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:04.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It was right to have her do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:07.25,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we draw lots?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:16.76,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.34,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.53,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when getting lost is fun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.24,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,but that must be because I get to meet someone new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:45.28,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Being alone... isn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.99,0:17:48.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:48.95,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.50,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:59.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you truly wish for it, your feelings will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.47,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.13,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That note will surely resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It will surely resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:09.56,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It will surely resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...and reach out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:18.19,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The fire maidens will not rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:22.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You embraced the demon, and suppressed the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the time to awaken before the people, your pain will{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.75,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,This sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:29.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the golden horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:31.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean the demon has...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.54,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,...awoken?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Please reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:49.14,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please receive my note!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.61,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:07.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The note resounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.37,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.17,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.38,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.05,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:26.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.84,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan on dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:32.68,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the Timekeeping Fortress, the post of Platoon 1121.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:33.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.91,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,About yesterday, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:53.33,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry for all the trouble I caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.58,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.12,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:19:59.09,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:00.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.80,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, don't be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:06.63,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it was all for this bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:29.57,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:31.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:35.87,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,A tale of why this fortress is called the "Timekeeping Fortress".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.62,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The notes of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.07,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:52.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:56.74,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to guide you as a trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:02.21,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in your care, Sergeant Major Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rio" is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:08.46,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Felicia's... I mean, our Captain's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:10.51,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't use ranks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:11.88,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:15.01,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.27,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's start right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:21.89,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,Try a morning bugle call for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:23.02,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:42.00,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl this time is pretty bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:26.31,SoraNoWoto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next episode: First Campaign - A Story of the Chair
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:26.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The radiance of this sky will carry to your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:36.22,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The melody you dreamed of is like serenity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:41.21,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}For your hands the dream is still far away, but
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.54,0:02:46.22,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}remember the voice so gentle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.54,0:02:59.03,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}That someone sung for you is happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:08.43,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}The sound of the skies echoes high over all sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:19.03,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Everything reflected in your eyes is the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:28.43,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}Even if you shed tears, you cannot stop here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:41.24,OP-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2.2\fad(130,130)}We're seperated a long way from tomorrow in the lights that rain without end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:58.10,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Pile up the feelings of love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.44,0:23:01.24,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Performing is also important
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:19.31,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I cried happily
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:25.26,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I laughed eagerly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:34.57,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}But all of them make me alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:38.71,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Let's walk slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.56,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:44.66,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Tell me why we dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.66,0:23:46.16,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}you just my friend
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:52.09,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Even if love and friendship change over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:57.55,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I want them to echo forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.09,0:24:04.06,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Speaking endless words touched by love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:10.01,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.03,0:24:14.64,ED-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}I can hear our harmony
